<subSubSection pageId="5" pageNumber="294" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1437,618,1689]" pageId="5" pageNumber="294">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,1627,1653]" pageId="5" pageNumber="294">Etymology.</emphasis>
This species is named in honour of Lithuanian entomologist Rimantas Butvila (Joniškis, 
<collectingCountry box="[1320,1429,1627,1654]" name="Lithuania" pageId="5" pageNumber="294">Lithuania</collectingCountry>
) who collected moths in 
<collectingCountry box="[419,490,1663,1689]" name="China" pageId="5" pageNumber="294">China</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
